"Tucano": "The ARKS of Retem challenge themselves in the Cocoons countless times during their training."
"And once they have completed training, they aim to complete them with even greater speed and precision."
"However, triumphing over every one of them is no easy task. To the best of my knowledge, only a small few can claim that honor..."
"I think someone as talented as you might just be able to do it too. Get out there and show your stuff."
